      <section class="home-section home-history-section" aria-label="Background">
        <p class="home-history">Most of my work has been in and around public health and global health ethics. <span class="home-place-note" tabindex="0" data-note="&hellip; non-consecutive">10+ years</span> of it now, with formative detours through ecology, hospitality, and amateur woodworking.</p>
        <p class="home-history">These days, I help people with the <em><a href="/consulting/#more-on-knots">knots</a></em> in their work &mdash; like the ones in wood, where the grain has to find a way around.</p>
